	<h1 class="title">「这世界」巴黎恐怖袭击后， 13个可能会骗到你的谣言</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4695/small/4695.jpg?1418026962" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">孙若空 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-16 12:45:01 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/17614/medium/17614.jpg?1447649044" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


